race.description: Bookmakers Charlie Osmetti & Ernie Mccreed Hcp (C2)
race.comment: While most of these struggle to win, CAP CAVOUR (1) has been in great form and looks the one to beat. Fresh-up winner here of his maiden then just missed last time. Low draw and will go close. BUSTER'S GIRL (3) is also going well, the latest finishing fourth in a Cl5. Well weighted with the claim and will take catching. SHINBONER (8) was placed fresh and on the heels of CAP CAVOUR. Fitter and can feature again. STEPCHILD (2) is a former Victorian who has changed yards again. Has won fresh and best Melbourne form would win this. Keep very safe. BRULANTE (7) should be ready to run well with the claim and the low draw fresh.
